result.name: The Charcoal Room

reviews.text: Nice food with reasonable price. Staff are young and polite. The seating is quite comfortable and not so crowded.

Very worth the price coming for a lunch set. Portions were very large and comes with a good selection of starters such as kimchi, Korean bean sprouts etc. Very comfortable environment to dine in and helpful servers. Will definitely come again.

I saw this place on instagram hk_foodblog. Found the address on google maps. After 12 hours of traveling to arrive in Hong Kong, spent a great deal of time looking for this place to have late dinner. We finally found the place around 22.00. At first, we were rejected by the staff, so we argued that on Google says your restaurant Closes at 23.00, only then was accepted reluctantly. Service could be improved.

Nice, it is a nice Korean bbq restaurant. You don’t need to read so detail on my wording. Take a look on my photos. How do you refuse to try if you are bbq lover. They event have out door area too (but not good when it is summer time)

Name of the place is a misleading as there is absolutely no charcoal used in the cooking. This is a standard gas grill.

Despite this, the meat quality is good, service is fair and they have a large outdoor seating area which is pretty cool

Interesting mall tailored for young people.

result.adr_address: 香港旺角彌敦道700號
result.name: T.O.P This is Our Place

reviews.text:
鋪頭都幾多 同埋好多都係唔同種類
但好似唔多岩男仔
上次同男朋友行個陣
佢都話無咩岩佢
這個都算是新開的商場，在假日的時間，人流暢旺，特別是很多家傭流連的關係，女洗手間多人使用不在話下，連wi-fi 都無辦法連上，那麼~管理層便要想法子提升網絡容量！
彌敦道700號位於香港九龍旺角彌敦道700號，樓高23層，1984年至2015年由香港政府持有，2016年起由領展房地產投資信託基金持有。 項目於2018年6月開業，商場定名為T.O.P This is Our Place。商場位處旺角核心範圍，將以年輕、活力、動感及帶領潮流打造旺角地標。
應有盡有，接連旺角中心，方便購物。 值得一提係T.O.P有個放空空間， 唔落雨可以去坐吓，感覺舒服。

result.formatted_address: 501舖, 700 Nathan Road, Mong Kok, 香港
result.name: 柞木炭家

reviews.text: Nice food with reasonable price. Staff are young and polite. The seating is quite comfortable and not so crowded.

午餐$148可選3種肉配牛肉飯，肉的品質不錯，生菜和泡菜可免費添加，泡菜好吃。地方乾淨舒適。海鮮煎餅比較普通，有點油膩。

光顅日期: 15 June 2019
午餐質優，豬牛肉都好味， 坐得舍舒適，抽煙通風好，價錢合理，但服務人手稍欠不足。
旺角食leisure lunch的好選擇，相較晚餐，lunch set 抵食選擇多，質優。環境舒適，店員友善。自選三款肉套餐$148。

Very worth the price coming for a lunch set. Portions were very large and comes with a good selection of starters such as kimchi, Korean bean sprouts etc. Very comfortable environment to dine in and helpful servers. Will definitely come again.
